<title>USA: Mesa Inc Q3 shr loss widens with charge.</title>
<headline>Mesa Inc Q3 shr loss widens with charge.</headline>
<dateline>IRVING, Texas 1996-10-24</dateline>
<text>
<p>1996			1995</p>
<p> Shr loss		   $1.20     loss	 $0.51</p>
<p> Net loss		  72,912     loss	32,473</p>
<p> Revs			66,752		   48,967</p>
<p> Avg shrs		  64,266		   64,050</p>
<p>	  9  MONTHS</p>
<p> Shr loss		   $1.11     loss	 $0.85</p>
<p> Net loss		  67,308     loss	54,320</p>
<p> Revs		     218,717		  170,388</p>
<p> Avg shrs		  64,125		   64,050</p>
<p>(All data above 000s except per share numbers)</p>
<p>NOTE - 1996 Q3 includes extraordinary charge of $59.4 million related to the early repayment of its $1.2 billion long-term debt, $3.1 million additional interest expense related to the defeasance of debt in the recapitalization and a one-time general and administrative expense of $5.6 million related to reductions in personnel.</p>
<p>-- New York newsdesk 212-859-1610</p>
